---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Terms of Service — AI Zest"
  description="AI Zest terms of service — rules and guidelines for using our website, content, and affiliate links."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    <!-- Breadcrumb -->
    <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#3B82F6]">Home</a>
      <span>/</span>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Terms of Service</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-10">Last updated: June 23, 2026</p>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        By accessing or using AI Zest ("the Site"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you may not use the Site.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Use of the Site</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes. You must not:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li>Use the Site in any way that violates applicable laws or regulations</li>
        <li>Attempt to interfere with the proper functioning of the Site</li>
        <li>Scrape, copy, or redistribute our content without permission</li>
        <li>Use automated systems (bots, scrapers) to access the Site</li>
        <li>Misrepresent your affiliation with any person or entity</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        All content on the Site — including reviews, comparisons, text, graphics, logos, and page layout — is the property of AI Zest unless otherwise noted.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        You may view, download, and print pages for personal, non-commercial use. Any other use requires our prior written consent.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">4. Affiliate Links & Third-Party Products</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Our Site contains affiliate links. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. We are not responsible for:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
        <li>The quality, safety, or legality of any third-party product or service</li>
        <li>The accuracy of third-party product descriptions or claims</li>
        <li>Any issues arising from your use of third-party tools or services</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">
        We recommend tools based on our honest assessment. However, we cannot guarantee that any tool will meet your specific needs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">5. Reviews and Ratings</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        All reviews and ratings on AI Zest represent our honest opinions. Ratings are based on our testing criteria at the time of review. Tool features, pricing, and performance may change after our review is published. We encourage readers to verify current information on the tool's official website.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">6. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        The Site and all content are provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis. We make no warranties — express or implied — regarding the accuracy, completeness, reliability, or availability of the Site. Your use of the Site is at your own risk.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        In no event shall AI Zest be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from your use of the Site or any third-party products mentioned on the Site.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">8. External Links</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        The Site may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or availability of those sites. We encourage you to review their terms and policies before providing any personal information.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">9. Modifications</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes are effective immediately upon posting. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">10. Governing Law</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the applicable laws. Any disputes relating to these terms shall be resolved in the appropriate courts.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        For any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#3B82F6] mt-2">
        <a href="mailto:admin@aizest.net" class="hover:underline">admin@aizest.net</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
